title: Watashi Konotabi, Oukoku Kishidan Dokushinryou no Kaseifu wo Suru Koto ni Narimashita
original_name: 私この度、王国騎士団独身寮の家政婦をすることになりました
sinopse:
Azusa Suzuhara moves to another world on the way home from overtime! In dangerous places, she was helped by handsome and beautiful knights, and was treated as like a princess. Even though she a has hobby of saving money, she is loved by the knights and the handsome prince?

(Source: Kadokawa, translated)
